com.facebook.buck.core.select

Class Selector<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.select.Selector<T>

  • public class Selector<T>
extends Object
    Keeps mapping of a single select expression. The keys of a mapping are SelectorKeys and the values can be of an arbitrary type.
